author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Hand safety tips…demo work is dangerous, especially for hands. I highly recommend the Ironclad Command Impact gloves. They have a cut resistant liner for the palm and back of hand. And flexible rubber guards protect the fingers, thumb, and knuckles. These gloves are worth every penny - you can find them at Ironclad.com…many thanks to Ironclad for sponsoring this tutorial and making excellent safety gear for workers 🔥
title: Hand Safety Tips - #shorts #homerepairtutor #brandpartner
